'''权利法案社会主义'''（{{lang-en|Bill of Rights socialism}}）是一种主张依据[[美国权利法案|美国权利法案]]建立[[社会主义|社会主义]]社会，或者通过制定新的“权利法案”以实现社会主义的理念。“权利法案社会主义”的概念最早由美国[[社會主義工人黨_(美國)|社会主义工人党]]于1976年提出<ref>{{cite web|title=The Socialist Workers Party Propose: A Bill of Rights for Working People|url=https://www.marxists.org/history/etol/writers/camejo/billofrights.htm|publisher=Marxists Internet Archive|access-date=2020-12-12|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323150645/https://www.marxists.org/history/etol/writers/camejo/billofrights.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美国共产党|美国共产党]]则倡导扩展[[美国宪法|美国宪法]]，增补有关加入[[工会|工会]]的权利、获得公平报酬的权利的条文<ref>{{Cite web|last=Miles|first=Roberta Wood, Dee|date=2016-05-01|title=Bill of Rights Socialism|url=https://www.cpusa.org/party_info/socialism-in-the-usa/|access-date=2020-10-14|website=Communist Party USA|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321131320/https://cpusa.org/party_info/socialism-in-the-usa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美国民主社会主义者|美国民主社会主义者]]也提倡权利法案社会主义<ref>{{Cite web|last=December 23|last2=2012|title=A Social and Economic Bill of Rights|url=https://www.dsausa.org/strategy/a_social_and_economic_bill_of_rights/|access-date=2020-10-14|website=Democratic Socialists of America (DSA)|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314192542/https://www.dsausa.org/strategy/a_social_and_economic_bill_of_rights/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

